erse as newspaper headlines (see attached link below) and various discussions on Facebook and web forums, a major strike is expected on 5th August (next Monday), with large scale assembly is also expected in our area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nWe appreciate your response by 8PM today (2 August 2019).<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5ze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=9e35e84d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"bfd9ff6f1ec1aa9cf4fbb246a9c4c737d560805c","tid":1393714,"uid":28860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"有冇物管tg gp?"},{"pid":"c0f711446de1f4af1129dc98a2bf1e3228e1f641","tid":1393714,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfd9ff6f1ec1aa9cf4fbb246a9c4c737d560805c","tid":1393714,"uid":28860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"有冇物管tg gp?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:53:26.000Z","msg":"好似無"},{"pid":"2b71028b2623f3f0d3809030ac97073d3b1d4daf","tid":1393714,"uid":2886